ta-ratio=\"0.5846153846153846\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ce84e53b-2b2a-4d48-cae9-04c701608800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"130\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 48px;height: 28px;\" data-index=\"24\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/91a7cc58-e3a9-4a05-97ad-30993ca69c1b/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"21\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 5.8%;\">纳入显著顶点集合<img data-imgfileid=\"503477568\" data-ratio=\"0.5375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6c373d3e-64bc-4dde-9479-2bfc2b220d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"160\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 36px;height: 19px;\" data-index=\"25\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/357abfb8-23dd-4e68-817e-c64ea4b21725/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"24\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.64%;\">，相连边缘产生的重复顶点仅保留一份：<img data-imgfileid=\"503477570\" data-ratio=\"0.16981132075471697\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c470c124-7376-4bea-9b47-4b8773ba9900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"742\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 147px;height: 25px;\" data-index=\"26\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/978a0b2c-b904-4176-9f7d-cace7076c64e/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"26\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 20.45%;\">。令<img data-imgfileid=\"503477572\" data-ratio=\"0.3401360544217687\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c23d0516-c1dd-492c-f352-ad355d280f00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"294\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 66px;height: 22px;\" data-index=\"27\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/9256a3a8-4b2f-48b9-846f-0eedcdde6087/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"25\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 9.38%;\">表示该集合中唯一几何顶点的数量。给定显著区域目标点数<img data-imgfileid=\"503477574\" data-ratio=\"0.43548387096774194\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f8e00d32-7987-43ec-f36f-f2c9c6654600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"248\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 75px;height: 33px;\" data-index=\"28\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0ae89ea7-9ef6-4f4c-a55b-022c0996b54e/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"27\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 9.49%;\">，当显著顶点过多时，通过最远点采样法 (Farthest Point Sampling, FPS) 进行顶点下采样；当显著顶点不足，通过对显著边缘增加采样来补充数据，从而得到显著区域采样点<img data-imgfileid=\"503477576\" data-ratio=\"0.676056338028169\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c700d125-a893-4ad0-bedf-f948b1073200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"142\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 36px;height: 24px;\" data-index=\"29\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d732729f-99f1-40af-af57-ca48d29c77f8/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"28\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.64%;\">。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"240\" data-imgfileid=\"503477516\" data-ratio=\"0.43425925925925923\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9071b338-82a9-45cf-969b-659f8f055800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 562px;height: 244px;\" data-index=\"30\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/4c0c0231-8e9d-431f-b35e-29fdaa0e27e5/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"29\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   基于 SES 算法，研究人员提出 Dora-VAE，在保持紧凑潜在表征的同时实现了高保真度的三维重建。为充分利用 SES 采样获得的富含细节的点云数据，研究人员设计了双交叉注意力编码架构，该架构在特征编码过程中能有效融合显著区域与均匀区域的特征表达。具体而言，研究人员沿用 3DShape2VecSet 的做法，首先分别对均匀采样点云<img data-imgfileid=\"503477577\" data-ratio=\"0.6865671641791045\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f9f299a9-8b98-433e-544b-80c6b8d1de00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"134\" data-original-style=\"height: 23px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 33px;\" data-index=\"31\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/eceb3b40-e657-4583-9159-cee77022aeff/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"30\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.85%;\">和显著区域采样点云<img data-imgfileid=\"503477578\" data-ratio=\"0.676056338028169\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c700d125-a893-4ad0-bedf-f948b1073200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"142\" data-original-style=\"height: 24px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 36px;\" data-index=\"32\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/1325e4d3-aaf5-4a83-8c27-e01ac3ee140a/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"31\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 5.59%;\">进行最远点下采样：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"14\" data-cropselx2=\"300\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"44\" data-imgfileid=\"503477579\" data-ratio=\"0.1398148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ebdc17b7-272c-4a2c-598f-ba6d0831b700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 233px;height: 33px;\" data-index=\"33\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f784bcdd-6069-4e4a-a203-402e51540aaf/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"32\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   其中<img data-imgfileid=\"503477583\" data-ratio=\"0.6049382716049383\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1eeafadb-1ca3-440b-9f2f-491d5a0a6100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"162\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 47px;height: 28px;\" data-index=\"34\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/9cb0b076-ed4d-4536-8ec9-df8f437d3a09/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"35\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 5.8%;\">与<img data-imgfileid=\"503477585\" data-ratio=\"0.6329113924050633\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5fbb2e84-45b4-458f-1613-26e2eb9bee00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"158\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 47px;height: 30px;\" data-index=\"35\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a02f7e4d-f350-48e9-ac00-83dc40229dca/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"36\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 6.22%;\">分别表示来自均匀采样点云<img data-imgfileid=\"503477580\" data-ratio=\"0.6865671641791045\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f9f299a9-8b98-433e-544b-80c6b8d1de00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"134\" data-original-style=\"text-align: center;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;height: 23px;width: 33px;\" data-index=\"36\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b9baf7e9-7ef4-4147-9801-6f7504fda656/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"33\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.85%;\">和显著区域采样点云<img data-imgfileid=\"503477581\" data-ratio=\"0.676056338028169\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c700d125-a893-4ad0-bedf-f948b1073200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"142\" data-original-style=\"text-align: center;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;height: 24px;width: 36px;\" data-index=\"37\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/49d83ad2-9077-4fbb-b93e-0ef5acfe910d/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"34\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 5.06%;\">的下采样点云数量。研究人员随后分别计算均匀点与显著点的交叉注意力特征:\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"59\" data-cropselx2=\"311\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"107\" data-imgfileid=\"503477586\" data-ratio=\"0.2898148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3bb169cc-f5a2-4f02-2db5-c93004a72300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 189px;height: 55px;\" data-index=\"38\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f90de94b-5318-4968-962e-9af9d525ee38/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"37\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   最终点云特征<em>&nbsp;C</em> 通过融合双向注意力计算结果获得：<img data-imgfileid=\"503477588\" data-ratio=\"0.3270440251572327\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e7f4ffa9-91f3-4dff-913b-5d44629ed600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"318\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 92px;height: 30px;\" data-index=\"39\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/29684fb0-82ce-4a57-91dc-e7729fbc2704/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"38\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 11.49%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   遵循 3DShape2VecSet，研究人员利用特征 <em>C&nbsp;</em>通过自注意力模块预测占据区域<img data-imgfileid=\"503477590\" data-ratio=\"1.0888888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc4666de-b1e7-4665-aa31-9fae4780cb00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"90\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 23px;height: 25px;\" data-index=\"40\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/df571990-abf3-4b29-a39a-2bde705eb30a/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"39\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 3.37%;\">，整个模型<img data-imgfileid=\"503477592\" data-ratio=\"0.8181818181818182\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c43d509-a17e-4c95-96bd-dd3a3fb93900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"110\" data-original-style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 32px;height: 26px;\" data-index=\"41\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a1b2aa16-4647-4fb3-8108-d19b8b1cc378/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"40\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 5.59%;\">通过最小化均方误差损失进行优化：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"18\" data-cropselx2=\"253\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"60\" data-imgfileid=\"503477593\" data-ratio=\"0.2212962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1cd968d7-5fe8-48cd-1fc3-9a3e177ff700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 223px;height: 49px;\" data-index=\"42\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7f2501c4-5f14-4a8d-9297-1a7a7b901e6a/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"41\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   研究人员通过三个指标评估重建质量：使用 1M 采样点对比输入网格与不同 3D VAEs 解码结果的差异，包括：1) F-score；2) 倒角距离 (CD)；3) 尖锐法线误差 (SNE)。为公平比较，研究人员同时给出潜在编码长度 (LCL)。结果表明，Dora-VAE 在 Dora-bench 中所有的指标都达到了最佳。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"155\" data-imgfileid=\"503477601\" data-ratio=\"0.2759259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d52780a1-6f6e-4688-abd1-56fb54ea9c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 562px;height: 155px;\" data-index=\"43\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/723c2a86-8fcd-4f68-a1b7-ea7ed7e1d817/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"42\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    <section>\n     Craftman3d开源代码：https://github.com/wyysf-98/CraftsMan3D/\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section>\n     Craftman3d项目主页：https://craftsman3d.github.io/\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section>\n   在训练 3D-VAE 的基础上，CraftsMan3D 通过汲取传统建模流程的经验，精心设计了两阶段的技术方案：第一阶段使用原生三维大模型进行初始模型生成。算法先使用 multi-view image diffusion 进行多视图生成，然后将多视图输入到 3D-DiT 扩散模型中来生成拓扑规则的几何和纹理。第二阶段为几何细化阶段，团队使用法向图超分的方案实现高质量法向估计，然后通过可微渲染实现法线图引导的几何细节优化。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"180\" data-imgfileid=\"503477518\" data-ratio=\"0.32222222222222224\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3ee4b8b4-6e49-4190-cbb6-71622da0bf00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 562px;height: 181px;\" data-index=\"44\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/dc6376a6-5184-4e82-ba92-219c7cc15f40/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"43\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>阶段一：基于 DiT 的原生三维大模型</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   团队提出了将三维扩散模型与多视图扩散模型相结合的原生三维生成方案。具体来说，算法使用 3D-VAE 将几何压缩到潜在空间，然后使用 3D-DiT 扩散模型在潜在空间进行生成。对于单个参考图像或文本提示输入，首先将其输入到多视图扩散模型中以获得多视图图像作为三维扩散模型的输入，然后使用三维扩散模型从中学习生成三维几何图形。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   团队设计了完善的数据筛选 - 几何水密化 - 渲染等数据处理流程，形成了强大的数据处理平台以支撑原生三维大模型的训练数据。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"381\" data-imgfileid=\"503477519\" data-ratio=\"0.6944444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/25c8f3b7-617a-4ce8-e84e-607c8fbd7600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 562px;height: 390px;\" data-index=\"45\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/eb6b779b-23e9-4165-a77b-07e2feab7167/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"44\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>阶段二：高质量几何细节优化</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   受限于 3D 大模型常用的隐式表达方案和 VAE 的压缩特性，原生三维生成的物体往往难以具备很高频的几何细节。因此，论文提出了第二阶段交互式几何细节优化，通过法相贴图生成和反向 “烘焙” 优化的方式捕捉高频的几何细节，从而产生高质量的三维资产。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"383\" data-imgfileid=\"503477520\" data-ratio=\"0.6824074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cf1a3bd4-7738-4c0c-9a70-9bf449000a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 562px;height: 383px;\" data-index=\"46\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b5d2e6c8-ec23-487f-9a7d-5bf04bf3e093/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"45\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   具体来说，该部分通过基于表面法线贴图的扩散模型来实现法线图细节增强，并通过显式三角网格优化增加三维几何细节。团队在原版 stable diffusion 的基础上使用法线数据集微调，并借助 tile 插件实现法相贴图的超分辨率生成。通过这种方式模型既拥有几何细节生成能力，还保留了原有的泛化能力。进一步基于法线贴图优化直接优化三维网格顶点，只需 10 秒，即可在用户绘制的区域添加几何细节，并完全保持其他区域的几何形状。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"285\" data-imgfileid=\"503477521\" data-ratio=\"0.5074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6d79b251-9e63-4d85-2a10-ec320369b300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 562px;height: 285px;\" data-index=\"47\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/fbf97d7c-a633-4411-b4ee-0c58ba5446b0/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"46\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   该技术还支持趣味扩展功能：以人物照片为输入，可生成与输入图像面部特征匹配的 3D 模型，实现 3D 资产快速换脸。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"503477522\" data-ratio=\"0.43796296296296294\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/14264afa-3749-4caf-5ca5-8f5c744da800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"width: 562px;height: 246px;\" data-index=\"48\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/08451808-1602-465d-8115-b944748514ca/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"47\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>使用Craftman3D三维生成技术方案，普通用户无需复杂操作即可快速搭建出精美的三维模型和场景。无论是游戏开发、影视制作还是建筑室内设计、具身感知虚拟场景，各类创意都能轻松实现。如下图所示，场景中的所有物体均由 Craftman3D 自动生成。</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503477523\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/69ee04bf-3836-4092-cb4c-cc9aa6609f00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"49\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3ef5259b-93a6-49b7-b7dd-59e90c31315c/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"48\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "香港科技大学开源 Craftsman3D 和 Dora 框架，以创新方法革新三维资产生成与编辑，其中 Craftsman3D 因其卓越性能获得 CVPR 2025 满分及广泛应用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "香港科技大学开源 Craftsman3D 和 Dora 框架，以创新方法革新三维资产生成与编辑，其中 Craftsman3D 因其卓越性能获得 CVPR 2025 满分及广泛应用。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了香港科技大学谭平教授团队在 CVPR 2025 上发表的 Craftsman3D 和 Dora 两项三维生成技术框架，并已开源。Craftsman3D 获得 CVPR 满分，并被 Roblox、腾讯等公司引用。Craftsman3D 融合了原生 3D 大模型以及实时几何细节优化两大部分，先由原生三维大模型生成初始模型，随后通过实时可交互几何细化操作，快速生成高质量的 3D 模型。Dora 模型则创新性地结合显著边缘采样算法与双交叉注意力机制，提升了三维变分自编码器（3D-VAE）的重建质量与压缩性能。Craftman3D 技术方案使得普通用户无需复杂操作即可快速搭建出精美的三维模型和场景，适用于游戏开发、影视制作、建筑室内设计、具身感知虚拟场景等。",
